Additional information from internal data sources is included to provide a holistic overview of compliance risks. Cross- functional knowledge exchanges take place at regular meetings, and an annual Corporate Compliance Risk Work- shop helps us identify and monitor emerging or changing risks. The results of the risk assessments are a key starting point for the ongoing development of our compliance system.

3.1 Compliance and ethics

Targets Our ethics approach is also embedded in our DEGREE

sustainability framework within the field of action Ethics.